<db:section xml:id="profile-prop">
<db:title>[read-only] profile : enumeration</db:title>
<db:para>This property holds the configured OpenGL context profile.</db:para>
<db:para>The possible values are:</db:para>
<db:itemizedlist>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-openglinfo.xml" role="deprecated">OpenGLInfo</db:link>.NoProfile (default) - OpenGL version is lower than 3.2.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-openglinfo.xml" role="deprecated">OpenGLInfo</db:link>.CoreProfile - Functionality deprecated in OpenGL version 3.0 is not available.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
<db:listitem>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-openglinfo.xml" role="deprecated">OpenGLInfo</db:link>.CompatibilityProfile - Functionality from earlier OpenGL versions is available.</db:para>
</db:listitem>
</db:itemizedlist>
<db:para>Reusable QML components will typically use this property in bindings in order to choose between core and non core profile compatible shader sources.</db:para>
